<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; background: #fff; }
    .accent-bar { height: 6px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5, #818cf8); }
    .container { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 40px; }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .brand { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #4f46e5; }
    .brand-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; }
    .doc-label { background: #eef2ff; color: #4f46e5; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 4px; }
    .parties { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .party-card { background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; }
    .party-card h4 { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .party-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #4f46e5; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .clause { font-size: 13.5px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .services-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .services-table th { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; text-align: left; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .services-table th:last-child { text-align: right; }
    .services-table td { font-size: 13px; color: #374151; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; }
    .services-table td:last-child { text-align: right; font-weight: 600; }
    .total-line { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; }
    .total-pill { background: #4f46e5; color: white; border-radius: 6px; padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
    .key-terms { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
    .term { background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px; text-align: center; }
    .term label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9ca3af; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .term span { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; }
    .signature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .sig-block { border-top: 2px solid #4f46e5; padding-top: 12px; }
    .sig-block .name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; }
    .sig-block .role { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; }
    .sig-block .date-line { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 8px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="accent-bar"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div>
        <div class="brand">{{freelancer.company}}</div>
        <div class="brand-sub">{{freelancer.email}} · {{freelancer.phone}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="doc-label">Service Agreement</div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties">
      <div class="party-card">
        <h4>Service Provider</h4>
        <p><strong>{{freelancer.name}}</strong><br />{{freelancer.company}}<br />{{freelancer.address}}<br />{{freelancer.email}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="party-card">
        <h4>Client</h4>
        <p><strong>{{client.name}}</strong><br />{{client.company}}<br />{{client.address}}<br />{{client.email}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>Project Details</h2>
    <div class="clause">
      This Service Agreement ("Agreement") is entered into between <strong>{{freelancer.name}}</strong> ("Provider") and <strong>{{client.name}}</strong> of <strong>{{client.company}}</strong> ("Client") for the project: <strong>{{project.name}}</strong>, commencing <strong>{{project.startDate}}</strong> and completing by <strong>{{project.endDate}}</strong>.
    </div>

    <h2>Services &amp; Compensation</h2>
    <table class="services-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Service</th><th>Amount</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each services}}
        <tr><td>{{description}}</td><td>{{price}}</td></tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="total-line" style="margin-bottom:16px">
      <div class="total-pill">Total: {{totalPrice}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="key-terms">
      <div class="term">
        <label>Payment Schedule</label>
        <span>{{paymentSchedule}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="term">
        <label>Revision Rounds</label>
        <span>{{revisionRounds}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="term">
        <label>Governing Law</label>
        <span>{{governingLaw}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
    <div class="clause">
      <strong>Intellectual Property:</strong> Upon receipt of full payment, all deliverables and work product created under this Agreement shall become the exclusive property of the Client.
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Both parties agree to keep confidential any proprietary information disclosed during the course of this engagement.
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <strong>Termination:</strong> Either party may terminate this Agreement with 14 days written notice. Client shall pay for all work completed up to the termination date.
    </div>
    <div class="clause">
      <strong>Revisions:</strong> This Agreement includes {{revisionRounds}} rounds of revisions. Additional revision rounds will be billed at the Provider's standard hourly rate.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-grid">
      <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="name">{{freelancer.name}}</div>
        <div class="role">Service Provider</div>
        <div class="date-line">Date: ____________________</div>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="name">{{client.name}}</div>
        <div class="role">Client · {{client.company}}</div>
        <div class="date-line">Date: ____________________</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">{{freelancer.company}} · This is a legally binding agreement · Governed by the laws of {{governingLaw}}</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
